{"tid":1086541,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人成功醫好過失眠？","createTime":"2019-03-31T23:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T01:31:21.000Z","uid":184103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"98368e6d3c99638d8de4cb4d798b6522146a3778","tid":1086541,"uid":184103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T23:53:35.000Z","msg":"平時十一點半訓 <br />\n平均都要成兩三點先訓得著<br />\n到第二日八半起身 <br />\n經常訓得五個鐘左右<br />\n而身體係明顯感覺到唔足夠<br />\n出現發冷 冷汗 胃痛 釣魚等症狀<br />\n<br />\n睇醫生佢開白瓜子比我<br />\n話食半粒可以訓到八個鐘<br />\n咁我有一排真係訓得舒服<br />\n十一點訓前食半粒 <br />\n一訓落去無耐就訓著左<br />\n但問題係食完就算訓足九個鐘<br />\n等二日都係勁攰 雖然上高既症狀會無左<br />\n但變左成日都諗唔野咁 對工作有影響<br />\n之後食哂個療程去覆診 同佢講個問題<br />\n佢又開返同一隻比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實有無人真係成功解決到失眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74cfe7839e50a18682c4a13d332b3a3ad3d30c0","tid":1086541,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T00:07:18.000Z","msg":"check T3 T4 range."},{"pid":"ee2bde37aced9f71913400c29133581c790f8ded","tid":1086541,"uid":184103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d74cfe7839e50a18682c4a13d332b3a3ad3d30c0","tid":1086541,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T00:07:18.000Z","msg":"check T3 T4 range."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T00:18:42.000Z","msg":"要去邊check?"},{"pid":"70f32451cb205c2892ba050d948817d666b327c4","tid":1086541,"uid":199549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:16:47.000Z","msg":"朝早7點半起身做gym 再返工<br />\n放工再打拳就解決到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f546bb57df1c13923e99da6c857739f06575f7","tid":1086541,"uid":36327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T01:18:19.000Z","msg":"去買鬧鐘，將部電話放喺第2度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個人而言係成功嘅"},{"pid":"142947aa6006cc162ee00a9d807fdba1f33c4d02","tid":1086541,"uid":184103,"like"